column44: InteractionID=2001447870Chatter's Name: MOHD AMIR BIN HASSANVOBB NO: drumah@unifibizLOGIN ID: 6087333339Contact number   : 0148889186????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Issue: vobb no dial tone????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Symptom (SPICE)):Performance degradation (HSI / VOBB).VOBB: Potentially down.Suspect service affected: HSI & VOICE.Propose Action: Reset Port.????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Advise/Action:*Next action (SPICE)):  CSP to add remarks in CTT[CAMELIA]: Fault Location= Customer Site Condition=Good Remark: Link is goodInbound:CSP to1) identified Customer actual issue.*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with telephone service ?'If YES:1) Click Config VOBB button if enable2) If Config VOBB button is disable create CTT activity NGN troubleshooting to TVA. Please refer guideline in WISER for Assurance - SR and CTT/TT Assignment Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=510&type=3If NO: follow steps belowAdvise Customer:1) identified Customer actual issue (CSP need to know either customer have single or multiple service issues. Example: HSI with IPTV or HSI with VOBB or all service failure).2) to OFF and ON back all equipment. (If not using VOBB)3) to check all cable connections.4) to perform Speed Test. (for HSI performance issue only if there are no results within 12 hours).Proceed with HSI Troubleshooting:*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with Wifi connectivity?'If Yes verify either customer unable to connected to Wifi SSID or low signal/slowFor Wifi SSID:1. CSP to confirm with customer on Wifi SSID .2. CSP to enable & configure wifi SSID & SSID password if needed. (agent need to asked customer the preferred ssid & ssid password.Rules: max 15 characters limit for password. 25 max character limit for SSID).For Wifi low signal strength/slow:1. Please refer troubleshooting in WISER Assurance >(Inbound) Speed & Wireless Issue Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=190&type=3>For HSI issue other than Wifi:1) Reset port. (if not using Unifi internet / VOBB).2) Reboot RG via ACS (if required).3) Proceed with performance troubleshooting.For IPTV issue:1. For UPB/STB to OFF and ON back IPTV equipment.2. Check cable (HDMI/RCA/Power supply) connectivity from UPB/STB to television set.3. Refer guideline in WISER for unifi TV and unifi playTV guideline and troubleshooting guide for Contact Centre TM1

column44: HERO ID:H-2508059501========================================Caller Name  (Call on behalf): JASNI BIN RIJANCaller Number:0146772742 ========================================Issue:======Additional Remarks: Internet down. Telefon set tidak d beri.SymptomPerformance degradation (HSI / VOBB).VOBB: VOBB potentially Down due to Last SIP Registration time was more than 1 hoursSuspect service affected: HSI & VOICE.Propose Action: Reset Port.Advise/Action:============ Inbound:CSP to1) identified Customer actual issue.*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with telephone service ?'If YES:1) Click Config VOBB button if enable2) If Config VOBB button is disable create CTT activity NGN troubleshooting to TVA. Please refer guideline in WISER for Assurance - SR and CTT/TT Assignment Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=510&type=3If NO: follow steps belowAdvise Customer:1) identified Customer actual issue (CSP need to know either customer have single or multiple service issues. Example: HSI with IPTV or HSI with VOBB or all service failure).2) to OFF and ON back all equipment. (If not using VOBB)3) to check all cable connections.4) to perform Speed Test. (for HSI performance issue only if there are no results within 12 hours).Proceed with HSI Troubleshooting:*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with Wifi connectivity?'If Yes verify either customer unable to connected to Wifi SSID or low signal/slowFor Wifi SSID:1. CSP to confirm with customer on Wifi SSID .2. CSP to enable & configure wifi SSID & SSID password if needed. (agent need to asked customer the preferred ssid & ssid password.Rules: max 15 characters limit for password. 25 max character limit for SSID).For Wifi low signal strength/slow:1. Please refer troubleshooting in WISER Assurance >(Inbound) Speed & Wireless Issue Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=190&type=3>For HSI issue other than Wifi:1) Reset port. (if not using Unifi internet / VOBB).2) Reboot RG via ACS (if required).3) Proceed with performance troubleshooting.For IPTV issue:1. For UPB/STB to OFF and ON back IPTV equipment.2. Check cable (HDMI/RCA/Power supply) connectivity from UPB/STB to television set.3. Refer guideline in WISER for unifi TV and unifi playTV guideline and troubleshooting guide for Contact Centre TM100. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=1333&type=3>4. If customer UPB is connected via wireless please refer troubleshooting in WISER Assurance >(Inbound) Speed & Wireless Issue Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=190&type=3>If the problem still persist after done troubleshooting:Refer guideline in WISER for Assurance - SR and CTT/TT Assignment Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=510&type=3>-call cust 8:20 AM

column44: InteractionID=2001447870Chatter's Name: MOHD AMIR BIN HASSANVOBB NO: drumah@unifibizLOGIN ID: 6087333339Contact number   : 0148889186????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Issue: vobb no dial tone????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Symptom (SPICE)):Performance degradation (HSI / VOBB).VOBB: Potentially down.Suspect service affected: HSI & VOICE.Propose Action: Reset Port.????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????????Advise/Action:*Next action (SPICE)):  CSP to add remarks in CTT[CAMELIA]: Fault Location= Customer Site Condition=Good Remark: Link is goodInbound:CSP to1) identified Customer actual issue.*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with telephone service ?'If YES:1) Click Config VOBB button if enable2) If Config VOBB button is disable create CTT activity NGN troubleshooting to TVA. Please refer guideline in WISER for Assurance - SR and CTT/TT Assignment Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=510&type=3If NO: follow steps belowAdvise Customer:1) identified Customer actual issue (CSP need to know either customer have single or multiple service issues. Example: HSI with IPTV or HSI with VOBB or all service failure).2) to OFF and ON back all equipment. (If not using VOBB)3) to check all cable connections.4) to perform Speed Test. (for HSI performance issue only if there are no results within 12 hours).Proceed with HSI Troubleshooting:*ask Customer 'Do you have problem with Wifi connectivity?'If Yes verify either customer unable to connected to Wifi SSID or low signal/slowFor Wifi SSID:1. CSP to confirm with customer on Wifi SSID .2. CSP to enable & configure wifi SSID & SSID password if needed. (agent need to asked customer the preferred ssid & ssid password.Rules: max 15 characters limit for password. 25 max character limit for SSID).For Wifi low signal strength/slow:1. Please refer troubleshooting in WISER Assurance >(Inbound) Speed & Wireless Issue Process Flow. <https://wiser.tm.com.my/SitePages/ContentDetails.aspx?ID=190&type=3>For HSI issue other than Wifi:1) Reset port. (if not using Unifi internet / VOBB).2) Reboot RG via ACS (if required).3) Proceed with performance troubleshooting.For IPTV issue:1. For UPB/STB to OFF and ON back IPTV equipment.2. Check cable (HDMI/RCA/Power supply) connectivity from UPB/STB to television set.3. Refer guideline in WISER for unifi TV and unifi playTV guideline and troubleshooting guide for Contact Centre TM1
